    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a joy to own. It\u2019s in really solid shape and runs like a dream\u2014perfect for someone looking for a dependable car that still looks great on the road. I\u2019ve taken good care of it, and it's totally ready for its next adventure! Feel free to reach out if you want to come by and take it for a spin!",
