    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_10_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_10",
      "description": "This E46 M3 is a driver\u2019s specimen powered by the S54 3.2L naturally aspirated inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a screaming 8,000 RPM redline. Power is delivered through a tactile Getrag 6-speed manual transmission and a factory M-Variable mechanical limited-slip differential. To ensure long-term structural integrity, the rear subframe has been professionally reinforced, and the double-VANOS system has been recently serviced for precise cam timing. The chassis remains composed with refreshed bushings and dampers, maintaining the legendary balance of the MacPherson strut and multi-link suspension geometry. While exhibiting minor cosmetic patina consistent with spirited use, the mechanical vitals are robust and track-ready. A turnkey performance icon for the purist who values mechanical substance.",
      "price": 34500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 31
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_9_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_9",
      "description": "Used car in good condition. Regularly maintained. Clean title. No mechanical issues. Interior is well-kept.",
