    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_6_listing_6",
      "firm_id": "sybil_6",
      "description": "Hey there! I\u2019m parting ways with my trusty ride, and honestly, it\u2019s been such a gem. It\u2019s in really solid shape, super reliable, and totally ready for its next adventure! I\u2019ve taken great care of it over the years, so you\u2019re getting a fantastic car that still has tons of life left in it. It drives smoothly and looks great\u2014perfect for your daily commute or a fun weekend getaway. Come take it for a spin and see for yourself!",
      "price": 34500.0,
