    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_7_listing_7",
      "firm_id": "sybil_7",
      "description": "This E92 M3 features the high-revving S65 4.0L naturally aspirated V8, an engineering marvel known for its 8,400 RPM redline and lightning-quick throttle response via individual throttle bodies. Power is delivered through a seven-speed M-DCT dual-clutch transmission and an M Variable Differential Lock, ensuring optimal power distribution and lateral grip. The chassis is equipped with Electronic Damper Control (EDC), allowing for adjustable damping rates to suit both spirited canyon carving and high-speed stability. Significant preventative maintenance has been performed, including the installation of treated rod bearings and upgraded throttle actuators, addressing the primary concerns of the S65 platform. Riding on a staggered setup with increased negative camber for improved turn-in, this car offers a visceral, analog experience that represents the pinnacle of the naturally aspirated M era",
